OL,3,CDanger of 'crying wolf' if flood
OL,4,Cwarnings are made too often, says NRW
OL,6,FThere could be a danger of 'crying
OL,7,Fwolf' if flood warnings are made too
OL,8,Foften, according to a senior figure at
OL,9,FNatural Resources Wales.
OL,11,FThe organisation has been criticised
OL,12,Fby some for not giving as early
OL,13,Fwarning as possible in the build-up to
OL,14,FStorm Bert which caused devastation in
OL,15,Fparts of Wales last month.
