OL,3,CDanger of 'crying wolf' if flood
OL,4,Cwarnings are made too often, says NRW
OL,6,FNRW's Head of Flood Incident Risk
OL,7,FManagement, Jeremy Parr, has been
OL,8,Fquestioned by Welsh MPs in the House
OL,9,Fof Commons today along with leaders of
OL,10,Fthe Met Office and the Flood
OL,11,FForecasting Centre.
OL,13,FMr Parr told the Welsh Affairs Select
OL,14,FCommittee that the Met Office issues
OL,15,Fweather warnings while NRW issues
OL,16,Fflood warnings.
