OL,3,CDanger of 'crying wolf' if flood
OL,4,Cwarnings are made too often, says NRW
OL,6,FHe said: "During those storms we
OL,7,Fissued a large number of flood
OL,8,Fwarnings across large parts of Wales,
OL,9,Fand the messaging around flood
OL,10,Fwarnings is important, and that
OL,11,Fconsistency of messaging is important.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/8
