OL,3,CDanger of 'crying wolf' if flood
OL,4,Cwarnings are made too often, says NRW
OL,6,F"We are really conscious of not crying
OL,7,Fwolf too often and losing the message.
OL,8,FSo it would be really easy to have a
OL,9,Flower threshold for issuing warnings,
OL,10,Ffor example, but with a lot less
OL,11,Fcertainty. And there's a real danger
OL,12,Fthere that people say, 'well, it
OL,13,Fdidn't happen, so therefore I don't
OL,14,Freally trust it for next time, next
OL,15,Ftime around.'"
OL,17,FHe also added that the message needs
OL,18,Fto be clearer that people have to take
OL,19,Fresponsibility for acting on warnings.
