OL,3,CDanger of 'crying wolf' if flood
OL,4,Cwarnings are made too often, says NRW
OL,6,F'Hindsight is a wonderful thing'
OL,8,FHe said: "The impacts from that
OL,9,Fmeeting were well understood by the
OL,10,Frespondent community. They were well
OL,11,Fprepared to respond, and the local
OL,12,Fcouncil for Rhondda Cynon Taf actually
OL,13,Fsaid they prepared like it was an
OL,14,Famber. So they think the impacts were
OL,15,Fwell understood. People have
OL,16,Funderstood our narrative.
OL,18,F"Hindsight is a wonderful thing. We
OL,19,Fwill certainly look at whether that
OL,20,Fweather warning was appropriate.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/8
