OL,3,CDanger of 'crying wolf' if flood
OL,4,Cwarnings are made too often, says NRW
OL,6,F"One of the things we are going to
OL,7,Flook at is, are there rare occasions
OL,8,Fbecause of the volume of rainfall,
OL,9,Fthat we step outside our National
OL,10,FSevere Weather volume practice guide,
OL,11,Fbut we are going to look at that and
OL,12,Fwe will not do that lightly."
OL,14,FRussell Turner, Head of Centre at the
OL,15,FFlood Forecasting Centre, told the MPs
OL,16,Fthat severe floods are now
OL,17,F"increasingly likely."
