OL,3,CDanger of 'crying wolf' if flood
OL,4,Cwarnings are made too often, says NRW
OL,6,FHe said: "I've been involved in flood
OL,7,Fforecasting for 15 years and it is
OL,8,Frelentless. I would describe it as we
OL,9,Fhave a series of events... We've had
OL,10,Ffive years which have been extremely
OL,11,Fbusy.
OL,13,F"It's difficult to benchmark exactly,
OL,14,Fbut I think these are increasingly
OL,15,Flikely events and familiar for a lot
OL,16,Fof communities, unfortunately."
